Package: soilquality
Type: Package
Title: Soil Quality Index Calculation with PCA and AHP
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Soil Science Team", email = "soilquality@example.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides tools for calculating Soil Quality Index (SQI) using 
    Principal Component Analysis (PCA) for Minimum Data Set (MDS) selection 
    and Analytic Hierarchy Process (AHP) for expert-based weighting. The 
    package transforms soil property data into standardized quality metrics 
    with comprehensive visualization and interactive tools.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    shiny,
    DT,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    covr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/soilscience/soilquality
BugReports: https://github.com/soilscience/soilquality/issues
